metadata.description:
#01 - Colors

Inspired by a never-ending life journey. Whatever happens, we just have to keep moving forward.

There is a lot of bad news in the world, but that shouldn't stop us from pushing forward. Making the world a better place is something I'm passionate about.

All of the artwork is created using a chain of AI Models that have been trained from the ground up and then computationally processed using Python Script.
